---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="hello, I'm Sophie Quinn-Graham"
  description="An update about who I am."
>
  <div
    class="min-h-screen bg-background text-foreground transition-colors duration-300"
  >
    <main class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen px-4">
      <div class="w-full max-w-2xl">
        <div class="mb-16">
          <div class="mb-12 flex justify-start">
            <div
              class="relative w-24 h-24 rounded-full overflow-hidden bg-muted flex-shrink-0"
            >
              <img
                alt="thisisme's profile picture"
                width="96"
                height="96"
                decoding="async"
                data-nimg="1"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                src="/avatar.png"
                style="color: transparent;"
              />
            </div>
          </div><div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h1
                class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-medium leading-tight tracking-tight text-accent"
              >
                hello, I'm <span class="whitespace-nowrap"
                  >Sophie Quinn-Graham</span
                >
              </h1>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h2
                class="text-lg font-heading text-foreground/80 contrast-more:text-foreground leading-relaxed max-w-xl"
              >
                my pronouns are she/her
              </h2>
              <p
                class="text-base text-foreground/60 contrast-more:text-foreground/80 leading-relaxed max-w-xl"
              >
                You may have spotted a few hints (I'm not great at being subtle
                when I'm trying to be), and I'm ready to share: I'm Sophie, a
                trans woman.
              </p>
              <p
                class="text-base text-foreground/60 contrast-more:text-foreground/80 leading-relaxed max-w-xl"
              >
                If you're wondering if I'm the person with a name you think you know, hi! I
                probably am. I'm also still married to a wonderful person named Patrick, so I don't have 
                negative feelings about that name - but we're both going to miss being "the two pats".
              </p>
              <p
                class="text-base text-foreground/60 contrast-more:text-foreground/80 leading-relaxed max-w-xl"
              >
                The real world is eventually consistent, so it's going to take
                me some time to filter this update across all the social and
                professional groups I exist in. I'm not going to get upset if
                you don't know this, but I'd appreciate you making the effort
                and updating any references to me that you might have.
              </p>
              <p
                class="text-base text-foreground/60 contrast-more:text-foreground/80 leading-relaxed max-w-xl"
              >
                You might want to go <a
                  href="/"
                  class="underline hover:text-foreground">Home</a
                > or to <a
                  href="https://cloudisland.nz/@thisisme"
                  class="underline hover:text-foreground">Mastodon</a
                >.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>
